OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FMinister defends safety law
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fon messaging apps          
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The technology secretary has defended a
OL,6, controversial section of the Online    
OL,7, Safety Bill which would force messaging
OL,8, apps to access the content of private  
OL,9, messages if requested by the regulator 
OL,10, Ofcom.                                 
OL,12,FShe said it was a sensible approach in 
OL,13,Forder to protect children from abuse.  
OL,15,FBut some tech firms, including WhatsApp
OL,16,Fand Signal, have threatened to leave   
OL,17,Fthe UK if forced to weaken their       
OL,18,Fmessaging security.                    
OL,20,FThe Bill is due to be passed in autumn.
